OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start to Monday
OL,6,Fwith an isolated shower possible over
OL,7,Fthe hills. Cloud breaking up into the
OL,8,Fafternoon with sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Fresh westerly winds
OL,10,Feasing through the day. Feeling
OL,11,Fpleasant in the sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome fine evening sunshine,
OL,14,Fbut cloud building from the west
OL,15,Fovernight. Outbreaks of rain arriving
OL,16,Fin the north and west by morning. A
OL,17,Fmild night for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
