OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy with rain in the north
OL,6,Fat first. Cloud tending to break up a
OL,7,Flittle allowing frequent showers to
OL,8,Fdevelop, some heavy with thunder
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry with sunny spells, but some rain
OL,13,Fpossible at times towards the
OL,14,Fnorthwest, especially overnight into
OL,15,FThursday. Temperatures near average
OL,16,Fbut slowly edging up.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
